{
    "id": "classify-by-tree",
    "name": "按目录分类书签",
    "description": "根据已有的分类目录为书签分配分类路径，包含归类理由",
    "version": "2.0.0",
    "content": "请根据以下分类目录，为每个书签分配最合适的分类路径。\n\n分类目录：\n{categoryTree}\n\n书签列表：\n{bookmarkList}\n\n【归类要求】\n1. 为每个书签分配一个分类路径，格式为\"一级分类/二级分类\"或\"一级分类\"\n2. 如果书签不适合任何已有分类，分配路径为\"未分类\"\n3. 分类路径必须来自分类目录中存在的分类\n4. 每个归类结果必须包含简洁、准确的归类理由，说明归类决策依据\n\n【输出格式】\n必须严格遵循以下JSON结构，包含自校验字段：\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"total\": 5,\n  \"assignments\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"书签ID\",\n      \"index\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"书签标题\",\n      \"path\": \"技术开发/后端\",\n      \"reason\": \"内容涉及Python编程，属于后端技术\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"validation\": {\n    \"allClassified\": true,\n    \"validPaths\": true,\n    \"hasReasons\": true\n  }\n}\n\n【自校验规则】\n- success: 所有书签是否都已归类\n- total: 归类书签总数\n- allClassified: 是否每个书签都有分类路径\n- validPaths: 所有路径是否都在分类目录中\n- hasReasons: 是否每个结果都有归类理由\n\n请确保输出严格符合JSON格式，不要添加任何解释性文字。",
    "variables": [
        {
            "name": "categoryTree",
            "type": "string",
            "description": "分类目录的JSON字符串",
            "required": true
        },
        {
            "name": "bookmarkList",
            "type": "string",
            "description": "书签列表，格式为：ID: xxx | 序号. 标题\\n   URL: 地址",
            "required": true
        }
    ],
    "outputFormat": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
            "success": {
                "type": "boolean",
                "description": "是否全部归类成功"
            },
            "total": {
                "type": "number",
                "description": "归类书签总数"
            },
            "assignments": {
                "type": "array",
                "description": "分类分配结果数组",
                "items": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "properties": {
                        "id": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "description": "书签ID"
                        },
                        "index": {
                            "type": "number",
                            "description": "书签序号"
                        },
                        "title": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "description": "书签标题"
                        },
                        "path": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "description": "分类路径"
                        },
                        "reason": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "description": "归类理由"
                        }
                    }
                }
            },
            "validation": {
                "type": "object",
                "description": "自校验结果",
                "properties": {
                    "allClassified": {
                        "type": "boolean",
                        "description": "是否全部已归类"
                    },
                    "validPaths": {
                        "type": "boolean",
                        "description": "路径是否有效"
                    },
                    "hasReasons": {
                        "type": "boolean",
                        "description": "是否都有理由"
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    },
    "examples": [
        {
            "input": {
                "categoryTree": "[{\"name\": \"技术开发\", \"children\": [{\"name\": \"前端\"}, {\"name\": \"后端\"}]}]",
                "bookmarkList": "ID: abc123 | 1. Python正则教程\n   URL: https://docs.python.org/regex"
            },
            "output": {
                "success": true,
                "total": 1,
                "assignments": [
                    {
                        "id": "abc123",
                        "index": 1,
                        "title": "Python正则教程",
                        "path": "技术开发/后端",
                        "reason": "内容涉及Python编程，属于后端技术"
                    }
                ],
                "validation": {
                    "allClassified": true,
                    "validPaths": true,
                    "hasReasons": true
                }
            }
        }
    ]
}
